dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Brandon Price. May I have your name, please?
Hello Brandon, my name is Lauren Turner.
Nice to meet you, Lauren. Can you please provide me with your date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my date of birth is December one nine eight five.
Thank you, Lauren. And may I also have the last four digits of your social security number?
Of course, they are seven eight two four.
Thank you for providing that information, Lauren. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Brandon.
You're welcome, Lauren. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
